首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973b0dd39d4a28349d5f66189ed3bea3ed31ab17","tid":1018613,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"雨巴出歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"4b9eb6208cd476d1e619eb4dfd4bdbc400a827ed","tid":1018613,"uid":231471,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"長年 加班加不到的月薪<br />\n捱窮 七仔碗仔翅也啃親<br />\n流行 的恤衫西褲貴得很<br />\n注定貧窮 終生因生計所困<br />\n<br />\n到節日 隨隨便便還是暴費<br />\n沒有財運 卡數來襲你就坐低<br />\n<br />\n銀包得一佰<br />\n銀行積蓄兩佰<br />\n連紅包都要拆<br />\n我窮到變壞做了鴨<br />\n搞野開房四佰<br />\n連埋單都要六折咭<br />\n有錢還 為何我們卻未能大發<br />\n<br />\n吃個飯 平平淡淡然後六佰<br />\n若吃牛肉 恐怕淪落到門市乞<br />\n<br />\n銀包得一佰<br />\n銀行積蓄兩佰<br />\n賠埋minpay五佰<br />\n我窮到變壞做了鴨<br />\n一世即將過百<br />\n旁人都早已做了賊<br />\n冇錢還<br />\n為何我們卻是頭垃圾<br />\n<br />\n從前曾自滿<br />\n笑前人們垃圾<br />\n誰人能料到月尾糧只得兩餐<br />\n<br />\n乘巴士三佰<br />\n成人加多四佰<br />\n連埋交租冇法<br />\n我窮到變壞做了鴨<br />\n卡數收息八佰<br />\n旁人都早已做了賊<br />\n<br />\n喂<br />\n天才<br />\n為何我們卻是頭垃圾？"},{"pid":"998cd75f3831a72d52baa650e91595432c654cdc","tid":1018613,"uid":231471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a59807ea789d9ca7812b2fbb5185e2229b48bb5","tid":1018613,"uid":199417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:23:10.000Z","msg":"天才兒童1985<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c978f7d87a59173e08713351d06da4cd2dc1bfd","tid":1018613,"uid":231471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"長年 加班加不到的月薪<br />\n捱窮 七仔碗仔翅也啃親<br />\n流行 的恤衫西褲貴得很<br />\n注定貧窮 終生因生計所困<br />\n<br />\n到節日 隨隨便便還是暴費<br />\n沒有財運 卡數來襲你就「慣」低<br />\n<br />\n銀包得一佰<br />\n銀行積蓄兩佰<br />\n連紅包都要拆<br />\n我窮到變壞做了鴨<br />\n搞野開房四佰<br />\n連埋單都要六折咭<br />\n有錢還 為何我們卻未能大發<br />\n<br />\n吃個飯 平平淡淡然後六佰<br />\n若吃牛肉 恐怕淪落到門市乞<br />\n<br />\n銀包得一佰<br />\n銀行積蓄兩佰<br />\n賠埋minpay五佰<br />\n我窮到變壞做了鴨<br />\n一世即將過百<br />\n旁人都早已做了賊<br />\n冇錢還<br />\n為何我們卻是條垃圾<br />\n<br />\n從前曾自滿<br />\n笑前人們垃圾<br />\n誰人能料到月尾糧只得兩餐<br />\n<br />\n乘巴士三佰<br />\n成人加多四佰<br />\n連埋交租冇法<br />\n我窮到變壞做了鴨<br />\n卡數收息八佰<br />\n旁人都早已做了賊<br />\n<br />\n喂<br />\n天才<br />\n為何我們卻是條垃圾？<br />\n<br />\n人人一出生早已選擇好<br />\n榮華富貴高攀也碰不到<br />\n如投 胎可使我更加好<br />\n跳落危樓 登天台的我知道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"701a3915376668791cfbb9959305a8936def2844","tid":1018613,"uid":178223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T19:27:58.000Z","msg":"咁你想點"},{"pid":"5661f00dbfbbb80669f4f75db4dd9727c58f7133","tid":1018613,"uid":140754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cf06ee21a4110758949eabe3ae9ca5f25794e90","tid":1018613,"uid":89538,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"仲以為 鄭裕玲果首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"無名氏三萬～～～～～～"},{"pid":"57ab716904f85822c6f09c9a275bbc333a2ef322","tid":1018613,"uid":3208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5661f00dbfbbb80669f4f75db4dd9727c58f7133","tid":1018613,"uid":140754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cf06ee21a4110758949eabe3ae9ca5f25794e90","tid":1018613,"uid":89538,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"仲以為 鄭裕玲果首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"無名氏三萬～～～～～～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:49:32.000Z","m